# WoeBoost
**Author:** [xRiskLab](https://github.com/xRiskLab)<br>
**Version:** v1.0.1<br>
**License:** [MIT License](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT) (2024)

![Title](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xRiskLab/woeboost/main/docs/ims/woeboost.png)

